Jenni Evans, News24 (iStock) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Johannesburg -&nbsp;A man was shot dead, and a woman was stabbed during an apparent armed robbery at a restaurant in Bryanston, Johannesburg on Saturday afternoon.ER24 said that when they arrived at the scene in Hobart road with other paramedics, they found a man who had been shot lying outside the restaurant. The paramedics started CPR but he died, said ER24 spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth. A woman was found to have been stabbed and was treated for minor injuries and taken to hospital. Further details were not immediately available. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.